# Dissemination of BI Tools, Reports, and Metadata Enhancements

1. New Power BI Dashboard Release
   - Sales Performance Overview dashboard now available
   - Access through the BI Portal
   - Training sessions scheduled for next week

2. Enhanced Metadata Repository
   - Updated data dictionary with new fields
   - Improved search functionality
   - Available in the Data Governance section of the intranet

3. Quarterly Financial Report Update
   - Q2 financial reports now include interactive charts
   - Accessible via Tableau Server
   - New drill-down capabilities added

4. Introduction of Natural Language Query Tool
   - Beta version of NLQ tool integrated with our data warehouse
   - Allows non-technical users to query data using plain language
   - Feedback requested during initial rollout phase

5. Metadata Tagging Initiative
   - New tagging system implemented for all BI reports
   - Improves searchability and categorization
   - Guidelines for tagging available in the BI documentation

</OUTPUT_TEXT>
